    "The observed trend was that moving from two to three inner nodes produced the greatest decline in RMSE, but the subsequent decline in errors was only asymptotic.",
    "Page 19 of 35 89 So, changing the ANN architecture by adding one additional inner layer as shown earlier in Fig. 9 resulted in a lower RMSE of 0.153.",
